history.proof: intros x y. unfold moreUpToDate. destruct (x <=? y) eqn:H1, (y <? x) eqn:H2. - hauto use: Nat.ltb_irrefl, Nat.eqb_eq, Nat.leb_refl, andb_true_intro unfold: orb. - hauto use: Nat.ltb_irrefl, Nat.eqb_eq, Nat.leb_refl, andb_true_intro unfold: orb. - hauto use: Nat.ltb_irrefl, Nat.eqb_eq, Nat.leb_refl, andb_true_intro unfold: orb. - hauto use: Nat.ltb_irrefl, Nat.eqb_eq, Nat.leb_refl, andb_true_intro unfold: orb.

exceptions.exn: In environment orig_base_params : BaseParams one_node_params : OneNodeParams orig_base_params raft_params : RaftParams orig_base_params x, y : nat H1 : (x <=? y) = true H2 : (y <? x) = true Unable to unify "true" with "(x <? x) || (x =? x) && (y <=? y)".

original: intros x y. unfold moreUpToDate. destruct (x <=? y) eqn:H1, (y <? x) eqn:H2. - reflexivity. - apply Nat.ltb_lt in H2. lia. - apply Nat.leb_le in H1. lia. - reflexivity.
